Better Capital Ltd. Plans Fundraising ‘in Coming Months’

-- B y   S t e v e   B a i l e y
-- 
2011-10-12T06:12:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/better-capital-ltd-plans-fundraising-in-coming-months-.html
Better Capital Ltd. (BCAP)  said it has 210
million pounds of capital under management and plans to pursue
additional fundraising “in coming months,” according to a
company statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
